Rating:
  - Playability : 40%  (indicating the percentage of games that might be
    interesting for average user (lower values are typical for general
    purpose CDs since people usually prefer to play only games of a certain
    genre, and aren't interested for just everything that is available)){p}
  - Lastability : 8 months...3 years (14 months being an estimated average){pp}

  - Overall     : Good value for the price of only 10 EUR. Recommended.
{pp}
